## ❌ Common Mistakes

### Mistake 1: Building from Project Root
```powershell
# ❌ DON'T DO THIS on Windows
cd C:\websites\VENTURE\easy-escrow-ai-backend
anchor build  # Will fail with error 123
```

**Correct:**
```powershell
# ✅ DO THIS instead
cd C:\websites\VENTURE\easy-escrow-ai-backend\programs\escrow
cargo build-sbf
```

### Mistake 2: Forgetting to Generate IDL
```powershell
# ❌ Assuming cargo build-sbf generates IDL
cd programs/escrow
cargo build-sbf
# This only builds the .so file, NO IDL is generated
```

**Correct:**
```powershell
# ✅ Generate IDL separately
cd C:\websites\VENTURE\easy-escrow-ai-backend
anchor idl build
```

### Mistake 3: Using Wrong Anchor Command
```powershell
# ❌ These fail on Windows due to path issues
anchor build
anchor build --features mainnet
```

**Correct:**
```powershell
# ✅ Use cargo build-sbf from program directory
cd programs/escrow
cargo build-sbf
cd ../..
anchor idl build
```

